page.title: 05 Theakstones engineering
page.content: Mr Theakstones company is in Beningbrough and it has been running for 9 years.He mostly makes farming equipment like,feed barrows,pig pens, drinking troughs,round bale loader. His newest machine is called{FM300 {Rake}it is used to make silage it is really an old machine that has been modernised to go on the front of the tractor it is able to go at high speed and it saves labour and fuel you can attach it in seconds it turns the leaf under and the stem up and it can be used with a round baler.
